<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.7">
<l>kāriṉampurai mēṉinaṟkatir muttaveṇṇakaic ceyyavā</l>
<l>yāramārva ṉaraṅkaṉeṉṉu marumperuñcuṭa roṉṟiṉaic</l>
<l>cēruneñciṉa rākiccērntuka cintiḻintakaṇ ṇīrkaḷāl</l>
<l>vāraniṟpavar tāḷiṇaikkoru vāramākumeṉ ṉeñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart will become [full of] love for the pair of feet of those who join [Him]</l>
<l rend="indent">– having the heart to join the one rare, great Light called Raṅga,</l>
<l rend="indent">Him with a pearl garland[-bedecked] chest, a red mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">white teeth [like] good, shiny pearls [and]</l>
<l rend="indent">a body resembling a cluster of clouds -</l>
<l>weep and stand with overflowing tears that trickle down.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
